fools ' parade is a 1971 american comedy film directed by andrew v. mclaglen and written by charles &lt;unk&gt; . the film stars lew cody , george " gabby " hayes , anne jeffreys , charles " chic " hayes , henry " chic " hayes , henry " chic " hayes , anne jeffreys , charles " chic " hayes , anne jeffreys , charles " chic " hayes , anne jeffreys , george barbier , and james gleason . the film was released on october 15 , 1971 , by metro-goldwyn-mayer .